sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant FastAPI
    participant Ollama
    participant Celery
    participant PostgreSQL
    
    Client->>FastAPI: POST /extract/entities (document_id)
    FastAPI->>PostgreSQL: Get document chunks
    FastAPI->>Celery: Queue extraction task
    Celery->>Ollama: Extract entities/relationships
    Celery->>PostgreSQL: Save extraction results
    Celery->>FastAPI: Task completion callback
    FastAPI->>Client: Return extraction data